{"tid":2300183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"連坐！日本新制交通工具車逼車 營業單位將受連帶停業處分","createTime":"2020-11-25T10:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T06:18:39.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1da56876529831904db366cd0432a390ed4a6635","tid":2300183,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:05:22.000Z","msg":"日本反制「逼車」行為新制將上路，未來營業車駕駛只<br />\n要逼車，除了駕駛本人須受罰，業者也將連帶受到3天到7天的停業處分。<br />\n <br />\n日本放送協會（NHK）報導，有關妨害其他車輛行駛的逼車行為，日本政府國土交通省將<br />\n從本月27日起強化行政處分，只要例如計程車、貨車及大客車等營業用車駕駛逼車，業者<br />\n將連帶受停業處分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011250180.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202011250180.aspx&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuws%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=7e0b12b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011250180.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"5ca7c0295dd15003dac064f966c7bdb6dd3a95bf","tid":2300183,"uid":246295,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"咩叫逼車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c915c5d4c491d5a3be61420fed0a8190a282804","tid":2300183,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5ca7c0295dd15003dac064f966c7bdb6dd3a95bf","tid":2300183,"uid":246295,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"咩叫逼車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:10:03.000Z","msg":"跟車太貼"},{"pid":"1024bb972a17e44e6919b607728a860d2aa66d28","tid":2300183,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5ca7c0295dd15003dac064f966c7bdb6dd3a95bf","tid":2300183,"uid":246295,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"咩叫逼車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:11:09.000Z","msg":"應該指推9人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos